{"tid":451490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【捍衛粵語】首本專研粵語之語言學專著獲頒北京大學王力語言學獎","createTime":"2017-10-29T09:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T15:19:25.000Z","uid":35221,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1470243e18df8e04c4df810e61ce7b6d09b3cab5","tid":451490,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22552658_1705690679465280_9170536432665516646_n.png?oh=7c7deb44d11c36a5399133c6d50a3154&amp;oe=5A7D5733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22552658_1705690679465280_9170536432665516646_n.png%3Foh%3D7c7deb44d11c36a5399133c6d50a3154%26oe%3D5A7D5733&h=392326a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《粵語語法講義》榮獲北京大學王力語言學獎<br />\n北京大學王力語言學獎（通稱王力語言學獎）第十七屆評獎工作已圓滿結束，經評審專家審讀和評選委員會評議，評選出六部二等獎論著，當中包括鄧思穎教授的著作《粵語語法講義》。<br />\n<br />\n::::::關於「王力語言學獎」::::::<br />\n由北京大學教授、著名語言學家王力生前捐款設立，每兩年舉行一次，授獎予對漢語、中國境內其它語言的現狀、歷史的研究有貢獻的中國學者。該學獎與中國社會科學院呂叔湘語言學獎齊名，是中國語言學界影響力最大的語言學專項獎。<br />\n<br />\n::::::關於《粵語語法講義》::::::<br />\n運用現代語言學方法，將粵語作為一個完整的語言系統，從詞彙、詞法、句法等方面，全面論述粵語語法上的種種表現，兼論粵語音系和各種拼音系統的異同。一方面可作為研究和學習粵語的教材，讓讀者對粵語的語言特點有較為完整的認識；另一方面，以讀者熟悉的具體語言事實來說明比較抽象的理論，做到既能介紹粵語特色，又能普及語言學基本概念，亦適合所有對粵語有興趣的普通讀者閱讀。<br />\n<br />\n轉自商務出版 Commercial Press Publishing Facebook專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cp.publish/photos/a.136694703031560.16736.132171226817241/1705690679465280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcp.publish%2Fphotos%2Fa.136694703031560.16736.132171226817241%2F1705690679465280%2F&d=jyirg4QFkV9BO7jd8cClNS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=89f903f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cp.publish/photos/a.136694703031560.16736.132171226817241/1705690679465280/</a>"},{"pid":"ad57c3ba7cd2e70c6ce133017f5188040f1e06cc","tid":451490,"uid":6352,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"王力先生本身都係操粵語，師從趙元任果時就有研究粵語"},{"pid":"4eb5b028bfdc5b66009f416983f31e86c3dcfdf8","tid":451490,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王力先生本身都係操粵語，師從趙元任果時就有研究粵語</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 內行人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今次頒畀思穎老師呢本書係有歷史意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6226ff49fc0f8b97661d378aacdee042556727","tid":451490,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會肯頒獎畀呢d書嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768b4918534d5b429e68e7c5779b7fbfd38956a1","tid":451490,"uid":47359,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"等睇五毛話粵語只係方言。冇影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁</span>"},{"pid":"50ae214305b9eb382fb26dbe7ff8367bd0cf35e1","tid":451490,"uid":35221,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會肯頒獎畀呢d書嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為本書真係非常高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n語法學研究係老師畢生心血<br />\n呢本書非常值得一看同研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal